data.description: GOLF PRIVILEGES INCLUDED. Welcome home to a life of luxury & relaxation in this exceptional BRAND NEW build by Shea Homes in the Encanterra Resort community. This 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom haven with office & 2-car garage has been built with all the upgrades you could want. Situated on a premium lot, this nearly perfect home is equipped with everything you need for an effortless move-in experience. There are no other homes available in this community at this price point that offers these amazing amenities! The lifestyle here is truly second to none; enjoy a separate adult pool and swim up bar, golf course, pickle ball & tennis courts, multiple pools, state of the art workout facilities, spa services & much more. Don't miss out on your opportunity to live in paradise - DON'T PASS THIS ONE UP!
